flowchart LR
    UserInput([User Input]) --> PlannerAgent[Planner Agent]
    PlannerAgent --> RetrievalTool[Similarity / Retrieval Tool]
    RetrievalTool --> CriticAgent[Critic / Evaluator Agent]
    CriticAgent --> HumanLoop[Human-in-the-loop Review]
    HumanLoop --> FinalOutput([Final Recommendation Output])

    subgraph Plan
        PlannerAgent
    end
    subgraph Act
        RetrievalTool
    end
    subgraph Reflect
        CriticAgent
        HumanLoop
    end

    PlannerAgent -->|Infer energy, valence, tempo, mood| RetrievalTool
    RetrievalTool -->|Score and rank candidates| CriticAgent
    CriticAgent -->|Reject or approve with confidence| HumanLoop
    HumanLoop -->|Final approval and user-facing recommendation| FinalOutput
